.IX Title "XML::XORT::Dumper::DumperXML 3"
.TH XML::XORT::Dumper::DumperXML 3 "2007-01-05" "perl v5.8.5" "User Contributed Perl Documentation"
.SH "NAME"
XML::XORT::Dumper::DumpXML \- Generic Dumper module to dump any database into XORT format XML file.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 7
\&    my $dump_obj=XML::XORT::Dumper::DumperXML->new('chado');
\&         $dump_obj->Generate_XML(-file=>$file_chado,
\&                                 -format_type=>'no_local_id',
\&                                 -op_type=>'' ,
\&                                 -struct_type=>'module',
\&                                 -dump_spec=>$dump_spec,
\&                                 -app_data=>$a);
.Ve
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
.Vb 1
\&        This is the basic module which dump any DB into XORT format XML file
.Ve
.SH "CONTACT"
.IX Header "CONTACT"
.Vb 1
\&        Pinglei Zhou, FlyBase fellow at Harvard University (zhou@morgan.harvard.edu)
.Ve
